<TD><H1><FONT COLOR="#ff0000">
	Project to Intercompare Regional Climate Simulations (PIRCS)
	</FONT> </H1>
<I>The mission of PIRCS is
to advance the status of regional climate modeling by
evaluating the strengths and weaknesses of limited-area
models and their component procedures through
systematic, comparative simulations.</I>
